### Data Warehouse

Inmon: Stage → EDW→ Data Marts

Kimnaff: Stage→ Data Marts

Data Vault: Stage→ Raw Vault →Business Vault→ Data Marts

Medallion Archi : Bronze→Silver→Gold

![image.png](attachment:dac5ac45-091c-478e-8379-150f5e71132f:image.png)

Bronze Layer :

Def: Raw, Unprocessed data as is from sources

Obj:  Tracebility & Debugging

obj Type: Tables

Load Method : Full Load( Truncate & insert)

Target Audiences: Data Engineers

![image.png](attachment:0336d474-e3c7-438e-87db-53d28d157f30:image.png)

### DDL: Data Definition Language

Silver layer:

Def: Clean & standardized data

Obj: prepare Data for Analysis

type: Tables

Load Method: Full Load( Truncate & insert)

Data Transformation: Data Cleaning, Data Standardization, Data Normalization, Derived Columns, Data Enrichment

TA: Data Engineers, Data Analysts

![image.png](attachment:d3eb55cd-2664-4e48-8e97-0757ebf76b4d:5f5939da-b50f-439b-b3b6-d21c2be63c99.png)

Gold Layer:

Def: Business - Ready data

obj: Provide data to be consumed for reporting & analytics

Type: Views

Data Transformation:  Data Integration, Data Aggregation, Business Logic & Rules 

Data Modeling: Start Schema, Aggregated Objects, Flat Tables

TA: Data Analysts, Business Users

